   "metadata": {},
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# 基于 MindSpore 2.7.0 + MindNLP 0.5.1 的真人照片转卡通案例\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"本案例实现：输入真人照片，输出指定风格图像（吉卜力、迪士尼、古风/水墨、钢笔素描）。\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- DEMO 链接（魔乐社区）：`https://modelers.cn/spaces/<你的空间名>/photo2style-ms27`\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- 代码仓建议目录：`applications/photo2style_ms27`\\n\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 1. 环境准备\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"请确保环境满足：\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- Python >= 3.9, < 3.12\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- MindSpore == 2.7.0\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- MindNLP == 0.5.1\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- CANN >= 8.1.RC1（推荐 8.3.RC1）\\n\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"!pip install -r ../requirements.txt\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 2. 导入依赖与推理管线\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"本案例中，图像风格化主流程由 MindSpore 张量算子参与后处理；MindNLP 可用于后续扩展文本风格理解。\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"import sys\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from pathlib import Path\\n\",\n",
    "    \"import cv2\\n\",\n",
    "    \"import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"sys.path.insert(0, str(Path.cwd().resolve().parent))\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from photo2style.pipeline import Photo2StylePipeline, parse_style_text\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"pipe = Photo2StylePipeline(use_mindspore=True)\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 3. 输入真人照片并选择风格\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"将 `input.jpg` 替换为你自己的真人照片路径。\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"image_path = \\\"input.jpg\\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"style_prompt = \\\"吉卜力风格\\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"style_name, reason = parse_style_text(style_prompt)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"风格解析:\\\", reason)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"result = pipe.stylize_path(image_path, style_name=style_name)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"plt.figure(figsize=(8, 8))\\n\",\n",
    "    \"plt.imshow(result.image_rgb)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"plt.axis(\\\"off\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"plt.title(f\\\"输出风格: {result.style_name}\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"plt.show()\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 4. 多风格批量对比（可选）\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"styles = [\\\"ghibli\\\", \\\"disney\\\", \\\"ink\\\", \\\"sketch\\\"]\\n\",\n",
    "    \"img_bgr = cv2.imread(image_path)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"plt.figure(figsize=(12, 9))\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for i, s in enumerate(styles, start=1):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    out = pipe.stylize(img_bgr, s).image_rgb\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    plt.subplot(2, 2, i)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    plt.imshow(out)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    plt.title(s)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    plt.axis(\\\"off\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"plt.tight_layout()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"plt.show()\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 5. 交互式 DEMO 启动\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"在项目根目录执行：\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"```bash\\n\",\n",
    "    \"python examples/app.py\\n\",\n",
    "    \"```\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"上传到魔乐社区后，将公开链接回填到本 Notebook 第一节。\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"import mindspore\\n\",\n",
    "    \"import mindnlp\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print('MindSpore 版本:', mindspore.__version__)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print('MindNLP 版本:', mindnlp.__version__)\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  }\n",
    " ],\n",
